This is  to inform you that Chandigarh University, AMAZON  shall conduct pool campus recruitment drive for the students of B.Tech.(CSE, ECE & EE) 2018 passed out and 2019 passing out batch. Please find the other related details of the drive.

 

Ø  Company Website      : www.amazon.com

Ø  About Company         : Amazon teams in India work on complex business challenges to innovate and create efficient solutions that enable various Amazon businesses, including Amazon websites across the world as well as support Payments, Transportation, and Digital products and services like the Kindle family of tablets, e-readers and the store. Company is proud to have some of the finest talent and strong leaders with proven experience working to make Amazon the Earth’s most customer-centric company. 

Ø  Date of drive             : 04th February 2019

Ø  Time                           : 9:00 AM (Sharp)

Ø  Venue                        : Chandigarh University,

                                         Gharuan

Ø  Eligible Stream         : B.Tech. (CSE, ECE & EE) 2018 passed out and 2019 passing out batch.

Ø  Eligibility Criteria     :

ü  Candidates must have a Bachelors or Engineering or related field.

ü  Excellent problem solving skills.

ü  Possess an extremely sound understanding of areas in the basic areas of Computer Science such as Algorithms, Data Structures, Object Oriented Design, Databases.

ü  Be able to write Amazon quality code in an object oriented language - preferably in C/C++/Java in a Linux environment.

ü  Candidate must have good written and oral communication skills, be a fast learner and have the ability to adapt quickly to a fast-paced development environment.


Ø  Position                    : Software Development Engineer

Ø  Job Profile              : Passionate, hard-working, and talented Software Development Engineer who can build innovative & mission critical system software applications & tools. Candidate will have an enormous opportunity to make a large impact on the design, architecture, and development of consumer products. Candidate will be responsible for delivery and support of large-scale, multi-tiered, distributed software applications and tools.

Ø  Pay Package                  :

 

